\c 10
\s Chiratidzo chaKonerio
\p
\v 1 Zvino kwakanga kunomumwe murume paKesaria, \add wainzi\add* Kornerio nezita, mukuru wezana wehondo yainzi yeItaria,
\v 2 Wakazvipira nounotya Mwari iye neveimba yake yose, waipa vanhu zvipo zvizhinji, nokunyengetera kunaMwari nguva yose.
\v 3 Akaona muchiratidzo pachena nenguva inenge yepfumbamwe yezuva, mutumwa waMwari achipinda kwaari, achiti kwaari: Kornerio!
\v 4 Iye akamutarisisa, akatya, akati; Chinyiko Ishe? Akati kwaari: Minyengetero yako nezvipo zvako zvakwira akakwira zvikava chirangaridzo pamberi paMwari.
\v 5 Zvino tuma varume Jopa kundodana Simoni unotumidzwa Peturo.
\v 6 Unogara nomumwe Simoni musuki wamatebwe, imba yake iri parutivi rwegungwa iye uchakuvudza zvaunofanira kuita.
\v 7 Zvino mutumwa wakanga ataura nayKonerio, wakati abva, akadana varanda vake vaviri nomurwi wakarurama pakati pavaimumirira nguva dzose,
\v 8 zvino wakati avavudza zvinhu zvose, ndokuvatumira Jopa.
\v 9 Zvino fume mangwana vachiri parwendo vava pedo neguta, Peturo akakwira pamusoro peimba kundonyengetera nenguva inenge yechitanhatu.
\v 10 Akava nenzara kwazvo, akada kudya; zvino vakati vachagadzira akabatwa nomweya;
\v 11 akavona denga razarurwa, nechimwe chinhu chichiburuka somucheka mukuru unoburusirwa pasi wakasungwa miromo mina.
\v 12 Maiva nemhuka dzose dzinamakumbo mana nezvinokambaira zvenyika, neshiri dzedenga.
\v 13 Inzwi rikavuya kwaari, richiti: Simuka Peturo, baya, udye.
\v 14 Asi Peturo akati: Kwete, Ishe, nokuti handina kutongodya chinhu chisakanaka, chinetsvina.
\v 15 ipapo inzwi rikavuya zve kwaari rwechipiri, richiti: Chakanatswa naMwari, usati, chine tsvina iwe.
\v 16 Izvozvo zvakaitwa katatu, chinhu chikakwidzwa pakarepo kudenga.
\v 17 Zvino Peturo wakati achakanganiswa mumoyo make kuti chiratidzo chaakanga avona chairevei, tarira varume vakanga vatumwa naKornerio, vamira pasuvo vachibvunza imba yaSimoni;
\v 18 vakadana, vakabvunza kana Simoni, unonzi Peturo, agerepo.
\v 19 Zvino Peturo, achafunga chiratidzo, Mweya akati kwaari: Tarira, varume vatatu vanokutsvaka.
\v 20 Zvino simuka, uburuke, uende navo, usinganyunyuti, nokuti ndini ndava tuma.
\v 21 Ipapo Peturo akaburukira kuvarume avo, akati kwavari: Tarirai, ndini wamunotsvaka; shoko ramavuyira ndereiko?
\v 22 Vakati: Kornerio, mukuru wezana, murume wakarurama, unotya Mwari, unorumbidzwa norudzi rwose rwavaJudha, wakarairwa naMwari nomutumwa mutsvene, kuti anzwe mashoko kwamuri.
\v 23 Ipapo akavadana mumba, akati vagarepo. Fume mangwana akasimuka, akaenda navo; nedzimwe hama dzapaJopa dzikamuperekedza.
\v 24 Fume zve mangwana akapinda Kesaria, Zvino Kornerio wakanga akavamirira, akakokera hama dzake neshamwari dzake dzaidikamwa.
\v 25 Zvino Peturo wakati achipinda, Kornerio akamuchingamidza, akawira pasi petsoka dzake, akamunamata.
\v 26 Asi Peturo wakamusimudza, akati: Simuka, neni ndiri munhuvo.
\v 27 Zvino wakati achataura naye, akapinda, akawana vazhinji vakavungana,
\v 28 akati kwavari: imwi munoziva kuti hazvina kufanira kuti muJudha afambidzane nomunhu worumwe rudzi, kana kuvuya kwaari: Asi Mwari wakandiratidza, kuti ndirege kuti munhu haana kunaka, kana kuti unetsvina;
\v 29 naizvozvo ndavuya, ndisingarambi, zvandadamwa; zvino ndinobvunza kuti mandidanireiko.
\v 30 Kornerio akati: Ava mazuva mana kusvikira nguva ino, ini ndakanga ndichinyengetera mumba mangu nenguva yepfumbamwe, ipapo ndikavona murume amire pamberi pangu, anenguvo dzinopenya.
\v 31 akati: Kornerio, kunyengetera kwako kwanzwika, nezvipo zvako zvarangarirwa naMwari.
\v 32 Naizvozvo chitumira vanhu Jopa, udane Simoni, unonzi Peturo; unogara mumba maSimoni musuki wamatebwe, pagungwa iye kana auya uchataura newe.
\v 33 Naizvozvo ndakakurumidza kutuma kwamuri; zvino maita zvakanaka, zvamavuya. Zvino isu tose tiri pano pamberi paMwari, kuti tinzwe zvamarairwa naShe.
\v 34 Ipapo Peturo akashamisa muromo wake, akati: Zvirokwazvo, ndinovona kuti Mwari haazi mutsauri wavanhu;
\v 35 asi parudzi rupi norupi, munhu, unomutya, achiita zvakarurama, unogamuchirwa naye.
\v 36 Ndiro shoko raakatuma kuvana vaIsraeri achiparidza mashoko akanaka orugare naJesu Kristu (ndiye Ishe wavose),
\v 37 imwi munoziva shoko iro rakaparidzwa paJudhiya rose, rakatanga paGariri, shure kokubhabhatidzwa kwakaparidzwa naJohwani;
\v 38 raJesu weNazareta, kuti Mwari wakamuzodza noMweya Mutsvene nesimba; iye waipotenyika, achiita zvakanaka, achiporesa vose vakamanikidzwa naDhiabhorosi; nokuti Mwari waiva naye.
\v 39 Nesu tiri zvapupu zvazvose, zvaakaita munyika yavaJudha nomuJerusarema; ndiye wavakavuraya, vachimuturika pamuti.
\v 40 Ndiye wakamutswa naMwari nezuva retatu, akamupa simba kuti avonekwe pachena;
\v 41 akasavonekwa navanhu vose, asi nezvapupu zvakagara zvatsaurwa naMwari, iyesu taidya nokumwa naye, amuka kuvakafa.
\v 42 Akatiraira kuti tiparidzire vanhu, nokupupura kwazvo kuti ndiye wakagadzwa naMwari kuti ave Mutongi wavapenyu navakafa.
\v 43 Vaporofita vose vanomupupurira kuti nezita rake mumwe nomumwe unotenda kwaari uchapiwa kangamwiro yezvivi.
\v 44 Peturo wakati achataura mashoko awa, Mweya Mutsvene akaburuka pamusoro pavose, vakanzwa shoko.
\v 45 Zvino vatendivokudzingisa, vakanga vavuya naPeturo, vakashamiswa, nokuti chipo choMweya Mutsvene chakanga chadururwa pamusoro pavahedhenivo;
\v 46 nokuti vakavanzwa vachitaura nedzimwe ndimi, vachirumbidza Mwari. Ipapo Peturo akapindura akati:
\v 47 Kunomunhu here ungadzivisa mvura, kuti ava, vakapiwa Mweya Mutsvene sesu, varege kubhabhatidzwa?
\v 48 Zvino akaraira kuti vabhabhatidzwe muzita raJesu Kristu. Ipapo vakakumbira kwaari, kuti ambogara mamwe mazuva.
